data.description: Looking for the perfect home? Your search is over! This home boasts of its 2,234 sq. ft. of living space on .164 acres of land. The front yard is beautiful manicured and mature. There are 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Your primary bedroom is quite large and the primary bath has dual vanities, separate shower, and a soaking tub. The remaining bedrooms are all of a substantial size also. The kitchen is spacious with an island and granite countertops and gorgeous cabinets. Enjoy your mornings in the breakfast room or in your formal dining room. You’ll have plenty of room to entertain with family and friends in your huge den/living room. Enjoy those cold evenings with the warmth of your gas-log fireplace. Need a quiet place? Enjoy your Home-office/study. Parking presents no issues with your 2-car attached garage and large driveway. Enjoy the manicured backyard surrounded by a full privacy fence. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
